## Integration with Hacker1

DaisyUI components can be integrated seamlessly with the Hacker1 design system, allowing for consistent styling and behavior across the application.

### Theme Consistency

The DaisyUI theme variables align with Hacker1's color palette to ensure a cohesive visual experience.

### Responsive Design

All DaisyUI components are responsive by default, aligning with Hacker1's mobile-first approach.
